| ---------------------- | ----------------------------- | --------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Mutually Exclusive     | Cannot happen together        | P(A ‚à™ B) = P(A) + P(B)            | Even or odd on a die   |                           
| Non-Mutually Exclusive | Can happen together           | P(A ‚à™ B) = P(A) + P(B) ‚àí P(A ‚à© B) | Red or King card       |                           
| Independent            | One does not affect the other | P(A ‚à© B) = P(A) √ó P(B)            | Coin toss and die roll |                           
| Dependent              | One affects the other         | P(A ‚à© B) = P(A) √ó P(B             | A)                     | 

